<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,374,476,501]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="222">Pandalopsis ampla</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation box="[381,601,476,501]" pageId="21" pageNumber="222" refId="ref27094" refString="Spence Bate, C. S. (1888) Report on the Crustacea Macrura collected by H. M. S. Challenger during the Years 1873 - 76. In: Murray, J. (Ed.), Zoology. Report on the Scientific Results of the Voyage of H. M. S. Challenger During the Years 1873 - 76, 24, pp. i - xc, 1 - 942, pls. 1 - 157." type="journal article">Spence Bate, 1888</bibRefCitation>
</emphasis>
